},{"pid":"99e17f4eec8895115269d6a5d04bc79eab6295f6","tid":1620550,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77e000c63d48a2824141856f173663910255032d","tid":1620550,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:46:06.000Z","msg":"紅色資本係主要敵人之一<br />\n燒一間鋪佢比得起，但係積少成多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:13:09.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"cf65b16438885179be3ea53f5ae8d957c40d71a4","tid":1620550,"uid":273892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"政府建築，但唔包消防同醫院"},{"pid":"ed9d50094aa9f0a6929f9f4e7c320778de3aee8c","tid":1620550,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好再係人地個框框入面玩啦<br />\n規矩人地定無可能會贏<br />\n出緊急法佢話抄你家就抄你家<br />\n香港人要跳出框框<br />\n宣佈現政府違法並成立臨時政府<br />\n再立即宣佈香港進入戰爭狀態<br />\n同時以臨時政府名義請求聯合國/美軍出兵<br />\n並承諾香港將承擔所有戰爭開支<br />\n籌備明年1月1日大選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1619715/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1619715/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1620237/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1620237/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1609431/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1609431/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c76e4b7a7248d681070cc2dc3986add6bed32625","tid":1620550,"uid":318752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:21:56.000Z","msg":"各位手足，我知大家今晚士氣高漲。<br />\n<br />\n但我知道今晚好多人都趕緊返屋企，唔會出來。<br />\n<br />\n所以，人數會有機會少過之前。<br />\n<br />\n同埋，一到12點，灰姑娘個魔法無左，班狗就會出來見人就咬。<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地捉到就一定告得入，唔駛就住就住。分分鐘仲會有bonus,，捉得愈多，分得愈多。<br />\n<br />\n但，無理由12點就自己除豬嘴咁笨柒。<br />\n<br />\n所以，見差唔多就好閃。班狗等左今晚好耐。<br />\n<br />\n長期抗爭，今晚不是end Game <br />\n<br />\nBTW, 小心班狗又開真槍。"},{"pid":"0ba204f55fb9075ae8da26857e444560ec11ab2b","tid":1620550,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c60d033507e97e22885f24f4e48018d6673e06e6","tid":1620550,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"因 係因為共產黨<br />\n共產黨靠咩補血 就係錢 香港人既錢 港元 香港既經濟地位 <br />\n我地就算有真普選 贏晒區選都冇用<br />\n共產黨最多做影子政府 一樣控制晒我地港人既命運"},{"pid":"db2c6d9f75efe8601a38fc0bcadd81b7e8e19c75","tid":1620550,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:30:12.000Z","msg":"長推"},{"pid":"e9bc30f055a4cdf3b9ff34825c196423faeb7538","tid":1620550,"uid":274812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"上亞厘畢道八婆間屋"},{"pid":"56a44fe6b90fa9fc6a11cb1234bbcb2594abfca2","tid":1620550,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tHoFyFp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtHoFyFp.jpg&h=2e4cafda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9f64de6620010b73ba6b1422eef141fc44e965e","tid":1620550,"uid":239384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"希望唔好咁多支線<br />\n但係點都好 唔想又有手足比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係時候又講番 be water ar!"},{"pid":"2ee3fd1d3e6b00efcb544b22b5c6a15d3bfb4589","tid":1620550,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:35:45.000Z","msg":"梗係紅先啦⋯⋯"},{"pid":"641547ba25befeb27b821b761404231ea40d16ca","tid":1620550,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:38:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f87821e2bb81a2f4624cb180f289b72c4eb24b96","tid":1620550,"uid":86837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></span>"},{"pid":"6370b1867d88df0395550d80aaef5f2d7eb6bdd5","tid":1620550,"uid":57868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:46:27.000Z","msg":"紅 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星火 98190979"},{"pid":"72076685d828c283646e34bc89a2d0f08d436806","t